Common.Highlight.Common.Text: GREAT EXPOSURE ON CITY CONNECTOR ROAD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
132-134 Sheridan Street

Zoning: Commercial

Land area: 1012m2* approx.

Frontage: 20m x 50m depth

+ Front reception - 80m2*
